{"tid":828739,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬雲：現在無法為美國創100萬職位","createTime":"2018-09-20T01:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T03:02:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0f7b4a01ac916fe39b4d430ff809e56ba6c39b27","tid":828739,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T01:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180920/large/1537405599_7bc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180920%2Flarge%2F1537405599_7bc3.jpg&h=b49b9bed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴創辦人馬雲接受新華社訪問，提及去年與美國總統特朗普會面時，曾經承諾將會協助美國新增100萬個就業職位，不過目前的局面，「已經破壞了原來的前提」，現在「承諾沒有辦法完成了」。對於馬雲的說法，網民直指這完全顯示中美企業家不同之處：「中國大資本家遵從政府方針，美國大資本家左右政府方針！」<br />\n<br />\n馬雲去年初與特朗普會面時，曾經表示希望在美國的業務擴展，為美國創造100萬個就業崗位。他對新華社表示，當時他的承諾是基於「中美友好合作，雙邊貿易理性客觀」等前提，馬雲表示，「當前的局面已經破壞了原來的前提，已有承諾沒有辦法完成了」。<br />\n<br />\n對於中美貿易，馬雲表示「兩國間的貿易，世界上的貿易確實需要完善，但是貿易不是武器，不能用來打仗，它應該是和平的推進器」，他表示不會停止努力，會努力推進中美貿易健康發展。<br />\n<br />\n馬雲的說法引發不少網民的討論：<br />\n<br />\nxiaoj86_97256：這是中國特色資本主義與美國正宗資本主義的區別，中國大資本家遵從政府方針，美國大資本家左右政府方針！<br />\n<br />\n牛朗劍麥柯：你應該先幫美國一百萬人就業，然後再說話就有分量了。<br />\n<br />\n這個農民來自北車塔：大統領對馬雲不感冒&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nSocrates520：就是因為你動作太慢，人家看出你沒有誠意。還怪別人！<br />\n<br />\n豬頭囉囉：馬雲這是美帝民主黨給國內大領導帶話投誠，還是國內大領導給美帝民主黨帶話逼宮啊？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180920/58702354\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180920%2F58702354&d=ejPMF%2FKsVkkqkU0aRqzJe6NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=17e97b70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180920%2F58702354&h=ecf59b03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180920/58702354</a>"},{"pid":"9fafbd0d72b412a1864c7ea8fae543c6d3592595","tid":828739,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你顧掂自己先啦"},{"pid":"7cce13227d3ba80fd72f1cf9202c42a78413c6d6","tid":828739,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:09:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75bc8b4aaee37dbc270dcfc3a605e831ab813ebb","tid":828739,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94a198d2484f848945fde8c9ad32fd350d71162","tid":828739,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fafbd0d72b412a1864c7ea8fae543c6d3592595","tid":828739,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你顧掂自己先啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}